1465 }

2381 YYDESTRUCT_CALL("cleanup: discarding token", ippool_yychar, &ippool_yylval, &ippool_yylloc);
2382#else
2383 YYDESTRUCT_CALL("cleanup: discarding token", ippool_yychar, &ippool_yylval);
2384#endif /* defined(YYLTYPE) || defined(YYLTYPE_IS_DECLARED) */
2385
2386 {
2387 YYSTYPE *pv;
2388#if defined(YYLTYPE) || defined(YYLTYPE_IS_DECLARED)
2389 YYLTYPE *pp;
2390
2391 for (pv = ippool_yystack.l_base, pp = ippool_yystack.p_base; pv <= ippool_yystack.l_mark; ++pv, ++pp)
2392 YYDESTRUCT_CALL("cleanup: discarding state",
2393 ippool_yystos[*(ippool_yystack.s_base + (pv - ippool_yystack.l_base))], pv, pp);
2394#else
2395 for (pv = ippool_yystack.l_base; pv <= ippool_yystack.l_mark; ++pv)
2396 YYDESTRUCT_CALL("cleanup: discarding state",
2397 ippool_yystos[*(ippool_yystack.s_base + (pv - ippool_yystack.l_base))], pv);
2398#endif /* defined(YYLTYPE) || defined(YYLTYPE_IS_DECLARED) */
2399 }
2400#endif /* defined(YYDESTRUCT_CALL) */
2401
2402#if YYBTYACC
2403 if (ippool_yyerrctx)
2404 {
2405 ippool_yyFreeState(ippool_yyerrctx);
2406 ippool_yyerrctx = NULL;
2407 }
2408 while (ippool_yyps)
2409 {
2410 YYParseState *save = ippool_yyps;
2411 ippool_yyps = save->save;
2412 save->save = NULL;
2413 ippool_yyFreeState(save);
2414 }
2415 while (ippool_yypath)
2416 {
2417 YYParseState *save = ippool_yypath;
2418 ippool_yypath = save->save;
2419 save->save = NULL;
2420 ippool_yyFreeState(save);
2421 }
2422#endif /* YYBTYACC */
2423 ippool_yyfreestack(&ippool_yystack);
2424 return (ippool_yyresult);
2425}
